WEBVTT

00:00.780 --> 00:02.950
Previously on "The Mist"...

00:03.020 --> 00:04.620
This way.

00:04.689 --> 00:05.890
Are you real?

00:05.960 --> 00:06.960
Put down the gun.

00:08.119 --> 00:09.660
No!

00:09.730 --> 00:11.836
Team want to celebrate
tonight. Do you want to come?

00:11.860 --> 00:14.130
Alex is not old enough
for a party.

00:14.200 --> 00:14.900
I'm gonna get you guys a drink.

00:14.960 --> 00:16.260
Okay.

00:16.329 --> 00:17.970
Adrian saw what happened.

00:18.030 --> 00:20.670
He says it was Jay.

00:23.970 --> 00:25.110
We need to get inside.

00:28.810 --> 00:29.910
We got to go!

00:29.980 --> 00:31.680
Adrian. Wait in the car.

00:34.680 --> 00:36.320
What are you gonna do?

00:36.390 --> 00:37.690
Find my wife and daughter.

00:37.750 --> 00:39.120
We're safe.

00:42.530 --> 00:43.800
It's coming!

00:43.860 --> 00:46.360
It's coming!

00:48.000 --> 00:54.074
